ch.uzh.ddis.katts.query.stream.grouping
Class VariableGrouping

java.lang.Object
  ch.uzh.ddis.katts.query.stream.grouping.VariableGrouping
All Implemented Interfaces:
Grouping, java.io.Serializable
public class VariableGrouping
extends java.lang.Object
implements Grouping

This Grouping sends the variable bindings always to the same group. The group can be build up on different variable values. The GroupOn indicates on which Variable value(s) should be grouped on.

Author:
Thomas Hunziker

getGroupOnVariables

public java.util.List<GroupOn> getGroupOnVariables()
The GroupOn defines on which Variable value should the groups be build. Each group is then processed on the same machine and in the same thread. This allows aggregation on certain values.
